title: WWI series will shed light on Eastern Front experience (KU - The University of Kansas) ...
text: ( Source : KU - The University of Kansas ) LAWRENCE - The lesser-known stories of World War I 's Eastern Front will be the centerpiece of a lecture series at the University of Kansas . The program is part of KU's World War I Centennial
